snippet.textDisplay: It's hard to understate just how significant this is. In the space of a day with a tech stack that I'm only loosely familiar with, I built an entire leave booking system that integrates with Entra ID, can run in Docker (or note), has the concept of managers and admins for dealing with leave approval using application roles (and the /directReports Graph endpoint), can email notifications and create out of office calendar appointments via the Graph API.
